Hello Chilliwack and neighbors,

Whether you need help with furniture setup, outside pressure washing, or a full-scale renovation, we got you covered.

At GELLERT Contracting we tackle small to medium renovation/remodeling projects, Handyman Services, and General Contract work.

Kitchen, Bathroom, Bedrooms, whole Suite, etc...

We are looking forward to getting your projects accomplished.
